snippet.title: Very Bad News For Amber Heard | Officially Removed From Aquaman 2?
snippet.description:
In this video, we are going to take a look at what has been going on with Amber Heard and whether the rumors of this new gossip is true or not. 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
____________________________________________

Amidst her lengthy and prolific legal battle with her ex-husband Johnny Depp, rumors have been circulating that Aquaman star Amber Heard would be fired from the Aquaman’s sequel. Recent reports from the legal battle have indicated that if Heard is found to be faking evidence against Depp, she could be heading to prison, which is a cause for worry for fans who were looking forward to seeing Mera in Aquaman 2. Hello and welcome.
